{"tid":941533,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"搭地鐵遇到嘅小事…","createTime":"2018-12-15T01:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T02:28:52.000Z","uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b1799a271b36db8ea9da2249b0fdbc1cf33333ca","tid":941533,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:04:55.000Z","msg":"話說我今日早上，搭地鐵紅色市區綫，車廂入面只有半滿乘客。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於車程途中，有一位身穿潮裝，耳戴防噪音音樂耳筒嘅年輕男人，<br />\n由車廂車頭位置，向車尾方向行走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中撞到一位中年女乘客，搞到呢位女乘客破口大罵成幾分鐘，<br />\n差D連三字經都爆出嚟。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果位男乘客依然故我，繼續行到車尾位置。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個就係我搭呢程地鐵，真實經歷嘅小事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你哋話，喺車廂內行走，算唔算冇禮貌?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2d81b24a3f354d2979b051f21d77b3c4e6a5d9","tid":941533,"uid":213441,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:16:45.000Z","msg":"紅色綫 荃灣綫咪荃灣綫"},{"pid":"264655704de9a6b66426150f1f99eed23a33a800","tid":941533,"uid":8528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:18:42.000Z","msg":"車廂行唔係問題！但就唔好撞到人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多廢中成日係迫到爆嘅時間左穿右插，煩到仆街"},{"pid":"1269e7f82a43220af5df6e2767f862ac55fb92bf","tid":941533,"uid":211727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:20:44.000Z","msg":"非繁忙時間咪行到我20cm範圍內我都覺得可以接受"},{"pid":"35c975f766b790e8b181d429b68f61bf33d08898","tid":941533,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:26:44.000Z","msg":"點解樓主會知佢車頭行到車尾?? 跟住?"},{"pid":"baeea3941817d7f415e19245ba67c1c5539a1471","tid":941533,"uid":50041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:34:10.000Z","msg":"有d撚屌明明夠位行都會撞到人，一係就唔肯兜少少路硬係要攝你企緊果邊經過，正撚一賤種黎"},{"pid":"8434f939ddbbe9de7c6f77fc98c5e49c5ba06160","tid":941533,"uid":200132,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:35:50.000Z","msg":"尋晚睇完香港人比人屈到終身監禁單野<br />\n今日再見到樓主既小事<br />\n有啲感慨<br />\n<br />\n香港人Hi親佢少少就想殺人咁款<br />\n但係自己香港同胞比人屈到要坐終身都唔會有咩反應<br />\n<br />\n唉⋯⋯"},{"pid":"e6d37eadc8d12499aa8c4c17603eaf2d4fa752d6","tid":941533,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35c975f766b790e8b181d429b68f61bf33d08898","tid":941533,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:26:44.000Z","msg":"點解樓主會知佢車頭行到車尾?? 跟住?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:02:06.000Z","msg":"當時我企喺第三卡與第四卡之間聯結位，當果位男乘客撞到女乘客後，<br />\n我就望往佢行到車尾車卡位置。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe215f3b7e41bfad16d266ab022432bf370788d","tid":941533,"uid":2280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6d37eadc8d12499aa8c4c17603eaf2d4fa752d6","tid":941533,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35c975f766b790e8b181d429b68f61bf33d08898","tid":941533,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:26:44.000Z","msg":"點解樓主會知佢車頭行到車尾?? 跟住?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:02:06.000Z","msg":"當時我企喺第三卡與第四卡之間聯結位，當果位男乘客撞到女乘客後，<br />\n我就望往佢行到車尾車卡位置。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:28:52.000Z","msg":"你咁都望到佢行到車尾，証明車廂都唔係好迫喎"}]}